name: Whmiscal Butterfly for Spring-Plum & Red
description:
Butterflies are a sure sign of spring.  This fun and funky one is sure to delight regardless the season.  A single butterfly is fused on clear glass, approximately 3" x 3" and hung with copper wire.

All are handmade so please expect some slight (and wonderful) variations.

See our separate listings for those cute little table stands.  :)
